      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEADLY STREET (2) was well fancied last time on the strength of the win two back but could only manage second (17.33) at this track. Can measure up this time. LIL MISS SOPHIE (1) was never in contention last time after losing her position early at this track, but prior to that won by a nose at this track (17.47) beating Mystic Pixel in a LS6 on June 25. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Expected to feature in the finish. FRECKLES MONELLI (7) recorded back to back wins before placing last time after copping a check in the run, finishing a 3 length third (17.39) in a Grade 5 at this track. Bold showing expected again. TINY TWIST (5) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
